SUMMARY:Chabad S. Clara - Passover Seder! (100+ attending)
DESCRIPTION:Mountain Jew\n🔒 Want to attend? This Meetup won't show location or tickets — full access is in the "About Mountain Jew" section below.\nCelebrate Passover in the warmth of Community! Relive the Jewish redemption from slavery & enjoy:\n\n* A Delicious Passover Dinner\n* Argentinian Brisket & Vegetarian Options\n* A Participatory Retelling of the Story\n* International Selection of Kosher Wines\n* Tasting the special Passover Delicacies of Haroset & Marror\n* Hand-Baked “Shmurah” Matzah from Israel\nEARLY BIRD Adult $45 \\| Standard $54 \\|\n——————————————————\n✡️ About Mountain Jew\nMountain Jew is a community exclusively for Jewish young professionals in the Bay Area. Jewish people make up less than 0.2% of the world's population\, so having spaces like this to connect with one another is incredibly meaningful — we kindly ask that this be respected.\nThis is where people don't just show up to events — they actually meet\, connect\, and build real friendships. From hikes to dinners to social gatherings\, it's a community that's active\, welcoming\, and easy to plug into.For the comfort and safety of our members\, full event details (including exact locations) are shared only with verified MJ members.\n➡️ Join us: https://mountainjew.org\nGet verified to access the full calendar\, RSVP to events\, and join the WhatsApp community.
